<item>
            <title>[DELTASPIKE-1256] CdiTestRunner ProjectStage setting doesn&apos;t work on Config</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DELTASPIKE-1256</link>
                <project id="12312820" key="DELTASPIKE">DeltaSpike</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If you try to use different ProjectStages with CdiTestRunner, then only the first one gets used for ConfigResolver. &lt;br/&gt;
So this ends up with ProjectStage.Production most of the times.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The reason is that the current ProjectStage gets &apos;cached&apos; inside ConfigResolver. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should do some performance tests to check whether we can get rid of that. Because the ProjectStageProducer already uses a cache anyway. So the JIT might level out this method call after a few seconds.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
